welcome_message_body: Welcome to Lake Magdalene, a charming city known for its beautiful lakes and warm hospitality. We hope you have a wonderful time exploring and experiencing all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport serves as the primary hub for all airlines and houses the majority of airport facilities.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving mainly domestic flights.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving mainly international flights.

terminals.name: Airside E
terminals.description: Airside E is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving mainly low-cost carriers.

terminals.name: Airside F
terminals.description: Airside F is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving mainly domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport, with no time or data limits.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is exclusively for military flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at St. Petersburg-Clearwater International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: Terminal 2 is a newer addition to the airport, serving mainly low-cost carriers and seasonal flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'PIE Free WiFi' in their device's network settings.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Executive Airport handles all commercial flights and provides a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Executive Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering exclusive services and facilities for VIP travelers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Whitted Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Whitted Airport is reserved for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for internet access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Municipal Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
